# QR Platby SK - Permissions System

## 🔐 Core Permission Architecture

The application uses a three-tier subscription model (Starter, Business, Professional) with feature gates implemented through Clerk Billing.

### Plan Structure
- **STARTER** (Free): Basic functionality with strict limits
- **BUSINESS** (€5.99/month): Enhanced features for small businesses
- **PROFESSIONAL** (€16.99/month): Full-featured unlimited plan

